{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/momardi/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"f786caec-7c82-550f-a096-c24fea4724ac","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://momardi.com\" target=\"_blank\">Launch website</a>\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://momardi-wp.herokuapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived v1 website</a>\n</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/3e53665fe627633e3a19172772d0c6f2/18e3b/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3e53665fe627633e3a19172772d0c6f2/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/3e53665fe627633e3a19172772d0c6f2/18e3b/1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>I built Momardi.com initially with a custom template for Wordpress, but after a couple of years, we moved it into the Ghost platform and built another custom theme. And then, after a few more years, I moved to a GatsbyJS platform.</p>\n<p>Momardi is the personal website of Tuesday Gutierrez. It showcases art exhibits in galleries / museums and also features articles about new artists.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 711.4%; position